  </div>

  <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
      <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-1">
          <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600">4.6</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">很好</span>
          <span class="text-sm text-blue-600">1334条 ></span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-right">
        <div class="text-sm font-medium">距您驾车5.2公里·19分钟</div>
        <div class="text-xs text-gray-600">近南山(地铁站)·南园枫叶大厦(南山大道) | 南山大道1039号</div>
